spec_data.Name: oflb-prociono-fonts
spec_data.Description:
A serif font created by Barry Schwartz

The name is pronounced "pro-tsee-O-no" and is Esperanto for
either "raccoon" or the star Procyon. The author prefers to
think of this font as a raccoon.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 03:12:29 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A text roman with standard and discretionary ligatures, class-based kerning
